comment:
He said believe all women. 
I am a woman and I know that women lie just as men do. 
Evidence should be believed not "all women".
commentable_entity.title: Remove Raven Smith from Vogue
commentable_entity.description:
Raven Smith has wrote a Vogue article titled "Why it's time to believe Amber Heard"

He quotes "It’s time to believe women – all women"

He is siding with Heard purely based on her gender alone. 

Raven Smith believes a man can't be the victim of domestic abuse.

These individuals are some what confused to why the whole world has sided with Depp? Let me explain then. The Trial is PUBLIC unlike the UK trial that was private and the only information the public could see was the BIAS media articles. These media stories were ALWAYS going to be bias towards Depp as he was suing the media and why would media run anything other than bias against you if you're suing them. Amber Heard got away with her lies in the UK trial. 

Depp pushed for the second trial to be public and Heard pushed against it ( I wonder why). Why would a guilty person sue her and want a public trial ?. This was a masterstroke by Depp. The world has watched and the world has seen now that Heard is the abuser and liar. 

Raven Smith needs removed from society. We need to support men just as much as we support women in domestic abuse situations. 

MEN CAN BE THE VICTIMS #JusticeForJonnyDepp

https://www.vogue.co.uk/arts-and-lifestyle/article/why-its-time-to-believe-amber-heard

comment: Amber Heard is a manipulative person who has lived her life lying to people.  In every way she should be accountable for her own abusive actions. She can continue to lie all she wants but there is hard evidence!
